                        <p class="tpr-article-content__paragraph tpr-article-content__paragraph--blog">It has been fascinating working with the award-winning team behind Renegade Stories on Trauma Room One, a new eight-part hospital series available on 5STAR. The series takes a look inside the gripping, high-stakes world of brain and spinal surgery at The Walton Centre in Liverpool, where some of the world's best surgeons fight to bring patients on the edge back to life.</p>

                        <p class="tpr-article-content__paragraph tpr-article-content__paragraph--blog">From major trauma emergencies to life-altering operations, Trauma Room One puts us on the frontline of life-saving surgeries - but it's not for the faint-hearted. The Walton Centre in Liverpool serves a population of 3.5 million people and is the lead NHS organisation using spinal robotics and one of the most advanced neurosurgery hospitals in the UK. This is extreme surgery like no other, where death is just one millimetre away.</p>

                       

